duction, offering a comprehensive suite of manufacturing services beyond just 3D printing, including CNC machining, vacuum casting, and sheet metal, all from an ISO 9001:2015 certified facility in China."}', '{}'::jsonb, NULL, NULL, false, true, '{}', '70ad71f3-c876-44f0-8cb6-d25f2c271283', '2026-02-05 13:01:41.981+00', 95, 0, '2026-02-03 09:03:19.200102+00', '2026-03-11 09:46:08.663983+00') ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
