serve engineers and businesses globally, helping to transform digital models into high-quality physical parts.","unique_value":"This supplier differentiates itself through dynamic automation for efficient sourcing, offering instant quoting and automated DfM feedback to identify design issues before manufacturing. They also provide online order management and a vast selection of over 90 high-quality 3D print materials and finishes."}', '{}'::jsonb, NULL, 'Not specified', false, true, '{}', '714df434-bfec-4dc7-8071-15b684e92414', '2026-02-11 08:00:28.774+00', 85, 0, '2026-02-02 12:22:49.614381+00', '2026-03-08 10:09:46.678516+00') ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
