 SLS, SLA, DMLS), CNC machining, injection molding, and sheet metal fabrication. Xometry serves diverse industries such as aerospace, automotive, medical, and consumer products, providing solutions from rapid prototyping to high-volume production.', NULL, '{}'::jsonb, NULL, NULL, false, false, '{}', 'f590f37f-8db5-439a-b4da-ee1b1a455a1e', '2026-01-20 04:00:08.654+00', 0, 2, '2025-11-11 14:58:48.660984+00', '2026-03-08 10:09:46.678516+00') ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
