prehensive 3D printing and design services, including FDM and SLA manufacturing, CAD design, 3D scanning, and reverse engineering. They also offer specialized 3D printer consultation and repair services for Northern/Central Michigan and beyond, catering to a broad range of clients from automotive to cosplayers."}', '{}'::jsonb, NULL, NULL, false, true, '{}', 'f590f37f-8db5-439a-b4da-ee1b1a455a1e', '2026-02-06 04:00:26.901+00', 92, 0, '2026-02-03 09:03:19.200102+00', '2026-03-08 10:09:46.678516+00') ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
